source:
TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Quest Sync<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
Seanard could use a helping hand in doing some much-needed repairs.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
オスタル厳命城のショーナードは、冒険者に城の補修を手伝ってほしいようだ。

source: TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_TODO_00<tab>Use the reinforcing mortar on the damaged walls.

TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_000<tab>Ho there! If you're not otherwise occupied at the moment, how's about lending me a hand or two? They've got me on repair duty, and what with the sorry shape this place is in, it's definitely not a one-man job.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_000<tab>そこの君、暇なら手を貸してくれないか？
折からの人員不足で、後方支援部門に人が回ってこないんだ。
どうか城の設備維持のため、補修作業を手伝ってくれ！

source: TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_001<tab>It's a simple enough task. Just take this here pail of mortar, find a couple of spots where the walls are looking ragged, and apply a healthy dab. Thanks, friend─what with our ranks thinned as they are, we need all the help we can get!
target:
TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_001<tab>脆くなってる場所に「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8F8F01 /var>」を塗るだけだ。
本当にそれだけでいいんだ！
俺たち工兵を助けると思って、頼む！

source: TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_010<tab>Truth be told, the whole fort needs a good patching up after what we've been through. But with supplies and manpower limited as they are, all we can do is focus on the places that need it most.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_010<tab>脆くなってる場所に「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8F8F01 /var>」を塗る。
ただそれだけでいいんだ！
どうか俺たちを助けてくれ！

source: TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_020<tab>I saw you hard at work out there, friend! I'll rest easy tonight knowing that some of the ugliest patches of our walls are looking as good as new.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_020<tab><var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8F8F01 /var>を塗ってくれたのか！
ありがとう、ありがとう！
本当に助かったよ、ありがとう！

source: TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_021<tab>Are you familiar with the history of the Imperative, perchance? It was built nigh on a century ago, by the elves who ruled Lakeland in those days. After the Flood, it's served as one of our bastions of defense against the sin eaters.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_021<tab>もともと、このオスタル厳命城は、
エルフの国家、レイクランド連邦が築いた城でな。
「光の氾濫」直後は、罪喰いとの激戦が繰り広げられた場所だ。

source: TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_022<tab>Yes, this fort's taken its fair share of beatings, but it stands tall to this day, watching over and protecting the Crystarium and its people. And it's our job to <var 1A 02 /var>keep<var 1A 01 /var> it standing─material and manpower shortages be damned.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_022<tab>それを補修しながら、使い続けてきた。
クリスタリウムの最終防衛ラインの一角なだけに、
施設維持も重要なのに、なかなか人手が回されなくて……。

source: TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_023<tab>'Course, we couldn't do it without the generous efforts of volunteers like you. I reckon you have a real talent for repairs─mayhap I could interest you in joining the guard as a full-time wall mender?
target:
TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_023<tab>いやはや、君みたいな「仲間」がいてくれて助かった。
これからも工兵の一員として、やっていかないかい？

source: TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_024<tab>Ahahaha! I jest, of course. I've already taken enough of your time today. Thank you, friend, and be careful out there.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZC001_03384_SEANARD_000_024<tab>……いや、冗談だよ、冗談。
はっはっはっはっ！
